data.description: New Year/New Address AND SELLER IS PROVIDING UP TO $10,000 towards Buyer's interest buy-down and a 12 month warranty at no costs to Buyer.  Looking for lots of storage? Check out this beauty located in the highly sought after Parkland West Subdivision situated on a sprawling 10,019 SQFT corner lot.  The large windows new LVP flooring and nicely designed layout of the home's main and upper levels highlight the seamles flow of the living areas. The living room leads up to a flex space, dining area and kitchen.  Off the dining area is a large deck and patio-perfect for entertaining or just hanging out and relaxing.  The upper level also boasts a full guest bath, guest bedroom and primary suite with 2 walk-in closets.  The finished basement has 2 bedrooms, full bath, laundry and a surprisingly Large Storage Area -MUST SEE - Seller is a licensed MT/ND Realtor. Call your favorite agent today!
